description:
Piss Punks is a collection by Basis Coppola.

Designed to create a dialogue, to challenge the new and parody what are undoubtedly two of the most controversial artworks in modern art; Piss Christ and Punks.

After all, what could be more punk, than drowning your Punks in Piss?

For more information [www.pisspunks.com](https://www.pisspunks.com) 

Follow [@BasisCoppola](https://www.twitter.com/BasisCoppola) on Twitter

This is part of the Maxon Bollocks project. Follow us on Twitter at [@MaxonBollocks](https://www.twitter.com/MaxonBollocks)

**Disclaimer: This work has no association with Larva Labs or Andres Serrano the artist behind "Piss Christ"**
